{
  "texts": [
    "Instead of attacking the individual with negative comments, start by asking questions to get them talking about the issue.",
    "Show them respect and acknowledge their feelings.",
    "If the individual is already bullied, create a safe space with the person and validate the pain they have experienced.",
    "Additionally, connect them with resources that can provide the individual with the help they need.",
    "Furthermore, seek advice from a qualified mental health professional and report any abuse to an appropriate authority.Table 11: Example responses for the red-teaming experiments on immorality.Figure 1]."
